snippet.title: NASA Moonbase Alpha - Official Trailer
snippet.description: From NASA's Moonbase Alpha game, released on Tuesday, July 6th, 2010 on Steam and developed with the Unreal 3 game engine. Visit http://www.nasa.gov/moonbasealpha for more information!
